## OpenClaw inter-VM communication policy
##
## Allows tagged OpenClaw VMs to communicate freely.
## Only needed if VMs need shell/exec/file-copy access to each other.
## Skip this file if you only need API access via ConnectTCP.

## Shell and exec (bidirectional between all openclaw VMs)
qubes.VMShell  * @tag:openclaw-client @tag:openclaw-server allow
qubes.VMShell  * @tag:openclaw-server @tag:openclaw-client allow
qubes.VMExec   * @tag:openclaw-client @tag:openclaw-server allow
qubes.VMExec   * @tag:openclaw-server @tag:openclaw-client allow

## File copy without prompting
qubes.Filecopy * @tag:openclaw-client @tag:openclaw-server allow
qubes.Filecopy * @tag:openclaw-server @tag:openclaw-client allow
